\newlabel{tab:w1}{{2}{5}{GLM-5.1 W1 (tuning window, 00:30--01:00 UTC). TTFT in seconds. Bold is best in column. Completed counts from proxy logs; success rate $\approx $84.2--84.6\%}{table.caption.12}{}}
